{"tid":2436316,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英：走到美國或搗亂立法會肯定排除「愛國者」","createTime":"2021-03-07T04:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T08:38:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"650a8208ffb2276c73d90787f62805654b1bedaf","tid":2436316,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英接受中央電視台訪問談到「愛國者治港」，他說完善香港選舉制度仍有很多工作要做，不會低估難度，被問到如何防範一些人扮演「愛國者」，他說會有一定的定義。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英：「我看有個比較簡單的做法，這個簡單的做法用排除法，當然我們的『愛國者』我們有一定的定義，但是不愛國者，甚至違反我們國家利益，危害香港利益的這些人是甚麼人，我剛才舉了些例子，比如跑美國的，或者在立法會裡面搗亂的，這些肯定要排除出去的，用這個辦法來解釋說明，我們的想法來確保愛國者治港這個工作，我看是比較簡單的。（會不會出現有的人去扮演愛國者的形象？）有這個可能，我們現在還在觀察。」"},{"pid":"1deb3ffc8d2c86bb6b2954306ea3a661b79b3489","tid":2436316,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=426449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426449&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=b365bea7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426449&h=ca4bf338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=426449</a>"},{"pid":"886bda3c0bec4a7584f2d1597b13c49884cb9ca4","tid":2436316,"uid":76804,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7b98d5/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190909/20190909_9c23b4b242b2d0f6d116GVGBElE0VcK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F7b98d5%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190909%2F20190909_9c23b4b242b2d0f6d116GVGBElE0VcK0.jpg&h=61e998e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成班高官仔女去外國學習洋鬼子思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 